>
  <p>
    avaTOK is a product of <strong>AvaGlobal International, Inc.</strong> — a Delaware corporation in
    the United States that builds AI-first digital products designed to understand communication,
    creativity, and human interaction. You can learn more about our parent company and the wider
    family of products at <a href="https://avaglobal.ai/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">avaglobal.ai</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>Our mission</h2>
  <p>
    Your phone shouldn't be a liability. Other apps hand your real number to everyone you talk to,
    miss the calls you can't take, and leave you digging through old chats for that one file. AvaTok
    fixes all three. You get an <strong>AI receptionist</strong> that answers on your behalf and
    takes voice messages, a <strong>private AvaTok number</strong> you can share freely while your
    real line stays hidden, and <strong>AI-powered messaging</strong> with Ava — your AI brain — in
    every conversation. One app, one account, your communication on your terms.
  </p>

  <h2>AI-centric by design</h2>
  <p>
    We are an AI-centric software company. Ava runs through everything we build — answering calls,
    finding your files, setting reminders, auto-replying while you're away, and pulling documents and
    email from your Google and Microsoft apps right into the chat. We believe AI should work on
    <em>your</em> side of the glass: assisting you, never auctioning your attention.
  </p>
  <div class="note">
    A note on AI: our products use artificial intelligence, and AI can make mistakes. We share more
    in our <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a>. We've also made our best efforts to use
    AI-generated imagery responsibly — if you ever find something objectionable, email
    <a href="mailto:support@avatok.ai">support@avatok.ai</a> and we'll remove it. It was never
    intentional.
  </p>

  <h2>What we value</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>You first.</strong> Your number, your calls, and your data stay yours.</li>
    <li><strong>Privacy by default.</strong> Share an AvaTok number, not your real one — and keep the scammers out.</li>
    <li><strong>Never miss what matters.</strong> Ava answers when you can't and keeps every chat on your radar.</li>
    <li><strong>Built responsibly.</strong> Privacy, safety, and honest AI are part of the product,
      not an afterthought.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>A global team</h2>
  <p>
    AvaTok is made with care by a distributed team of builders across the USA, India, the UK,
    Germany, and Vietnam. Want to help build the future of personal AI communication? See our
    <a href="/careers">open roles</a>.
  </p>

